com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.handlers

Class SCUIXAPIMashupLeaf

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.handlers.SCUIXAPIMashupLeaf

  • public class SCUIXAPIMashupLeaf
extends java.lang.Object
    SCUIXAPIMashupLeaf class contains all the leaf mashups in the aggregate mashup. The leaf mashup contains its metadata as SCUIXAPIMashupLeafMetaData. This is used by SCUIXAPIAggregatorMashupHandler to flatten the aggregate mashup and the create input element from the request. The SCUIXAPIMashupHandler uses this object to get the per request based input and merging it with the mashup definition. The object for this class will change per request. rasrinivasan
